    {
        "content": "<p>Ooh, I think that's because <code>+</code> is now <code>HAdd.hAdd</code> so there's the indirection <code>HAdd</code>-&gt;<code>Add</code>-&gt;<code>AddSemigroup</code> which breaks the unfolding here.</p>",
